          <h1>Live Video-Streaming in Android</h1>
          <p>
            With the cine.io Android SDK, you can publish live RTMP streams
            right from your Android-powered phone or tablet. The h.264 and AAC
            encoding happens in a hardware-accelerated way, so you don't need
            to worry about battery life. Our backend handles the conversion to
            HLS for consumption on any compatible device. Write your code in
            Java as you normally would.
          </p>
